{"tid":519111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【欠租羅生門後…】連詩雅母疑被貼街招 指投資金礦涉非法轉移財產","createTime":"2018-01-04T04:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T05:31:51.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c29fbfe360583a53ce3b1e948b22874066ea1212","tid":519111,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"【欠租羅生門後&hellip;】連詩雅母疑被貼街招 指投資金礦涉非法轉移財產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連詩雅(Shiga)入行7年，主力唱歌，間唔中客串演出，16歲時，雙親離婚，Shiga自此同媽咪相依為命(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2EIhsTe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EIhsTe&d=zqmUZlESaYiEDOAqy4fqzsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=18ba4c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2EIhsTe</a>)，現居九龍塘筆架山道千幾呎連天台單位。<br />\n<br />\n日前Shiga業主好友陳先生向《蘋果》爆料，報稱Shiga疑欠租三個月，每月租金$45,000，涉及金額約13.5萬港元，之不過Shiga回覆《蘋果》否認欠租一事，問到經濟上係咪冇問題？Shiga話：「係啊，OK。」<br />\n<br />\n忽然爆出欠租羅生門，點知一單未完，一單又起，噚日《蘋果》影到連詩雅媽咪疑似被人喺九龍塘火車站貼街招，自稱金礦苦主聲稱Shiga媽咪唐X琦涉非法集資同非法轉移財產，以兩間公司名義，於市場集資千萬投資馬來西亞金礦，揚言「在未經投資者全部同意下秘密把馬來西亞金礦轉移到連詩雅名下」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向Shiga求證，不過電話一響即cut線，而佢嘅經理人則代回覆：「唔得閒，遲啲再覆!」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180104/57660746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180104%2F57660746&d=zqmUZlESaYiEDOAqy4fqzsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=328bd043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180104%2F57660746&h=f4ce1f3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180104/57660746</a>"},{"pid":"18fcf02851c93138c8e9b5659d045c94de451a9d","tid":519111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"699cf50f1905a5eb7b2a333e73e24d573a14bbf2","tid":519111,"uid":123083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"一波未平 一波又起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007b92e7cfb388c583a5818d1bb4361ab29e9456","tid":519111,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ff0b1f78f2565631b5386786f0e03f8dc1a544c5","tid":519111,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313572e10c15f265f3ae09f5c7608b60ff59cab1","tid":519111,"uid":16878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699cf50f1905a5eb7b2a333e73e24d573a14bbf2","tid":519111,"uid":123083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"一波未平 一波又起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"有波咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba98e8834d034165e9e7d11c9b155add57f3c98","tid":519111,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"如果係真<br />\n只係佢個女未去馬來西亞ja ma<br />\n你地投資緊架喇<br />\n暫時未有回報姐 等下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116ad4865dc857a0d288bbd2ac7014d8c3fa0ab9","tid":519111,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"可能公廁知情添呀 拉尻曬公廁兩母女去坐監"}]}